values: Karmas a bitch and my father is learning first hand what its like. The war at home has gone farther then it ever has. Even I stepped off the sidelines. Every time I'm around both of them I feel like I'm at court and the attorney is asking me questions. Depending on my answers ones going away. I hate myself for wanting my parents to get divorced but I'm tired of hearing there shit. If Dad stays around I know that next month I'll be back in the same spot, But if they separate finally I might have a chance to leave this hellhole or at least improve my life some. These are terrible times we live in, my grandmama got hit by a drunk driver a few months back and nows a vegetable. The Fucker got away with it and only had to pay about 15k for the entire thing. Fuck that. Now that I remember the my old folks my grandpapa is not looking so well but its mostly his fault. He just won't listen to the Docs. I need to escape or at least for someone to come rescue me. And I guess the good news is, I'm the healthiest I've been since I was 16! w00t! And I have a pet now to. A kitten that I named Foxy. Shes a bitch.

But it seems these days I'm only bored...
